textContent:
---support system---

We've had a very very fun date yesterday tas ngayon di kita makikita for three days straight. :((((. Naiiyak ako just by thinking about it. Nasanay ako ulit ma nakikita ka lagi araw araw, na andyan ka lagi sa tabi ko any time araw araw huhu. Kaya ang hirap hirap na isipin yung fact na di kita makikita for three days. Tapos lalo na, stressed ako ss resignation ko and kinakabahan sa new job huhu. I crave for your presence and comfort that you never fail to give me all the more tuloy. :(((. I miss you bbycakes. I love you so much.

---ayaw tayo ih---

We've also had one of our biggest arguements this week. And i just find it cute paren na even if we've known each other for 5 months na niyan, di paren tayo nagkakaroon talaga ng super lala na away. Di naman sa dinodownplay ko yung nangyari this week, pero gets mo yon? Huhu. Walang sigawan. Walang sinabing hurtful words. Ganern. I'm so lucky with you! You're so thoughtful, so caring, and so sweet. My world is a lot better because you're in it.
